  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ComparisonChart

    Chart

    SingleChart
    Class with functionality to display entries from one dataset.

Package org.pikater.web.visualisation.implementation.charts Description

This package contains classes, that implement the functionality to display scatter plots for input datasets.

These scatter plots can be created for one dataset or to compare two datasets.

See Also:
SingleChart, ComparisonChart
